title: Power 2015: The most powerful people in Australia
text:
AFR Magazine Power Issue Malcolm Turnbull is in, Tony Abbott is out.
It's our annual list of the most powerful people in Australia.
See how the AFR Magazine's Power panel ranked the 39 most powerful people in Australia over the past 12 months.
Explore our interactive below to find out who made the list.

The AFR Magazine Power issue, out Friday September 25 inside The Australian Financial Review.
